node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Lola Tash and Nicole Argiris on September 03, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'evan nicole brown @theevanarysays I think everybody deserves 6 months off of work to focus on the world crumbling around us maybe more'.

Photo by Lola Tash and Nicole Argiris on September 02, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Almost left the grocery store without buying a bag of spring mix to throw, unopened, into the garbage in two weeks.'.

Photo by Lola Tash and Nicole Argiris on September 02, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and text that says 'Me on my way to tell my best friend something I'm not supposed to tell anybody @heavyvanilla'.
Photo by Lola Tash and Nicole Argiris on September 01, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'It might be called social media but all I do is share memes and ignore people'.

Photo by Lola Tash and Nicole Argiris on September 01, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'I don't even have a sense of humor anymore it's literally just sarcasm and general loathing for the majority of the human population.'.

node.text: Hate hate hate double hate LOATHE entirely @mybestiesays

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Lola Tash and Nicole Argiris on August 31, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'if you see me talking to myself.I'm having a staff meeting.'.

node.text: If you see me talking to myself, no you didn’t @mytherapisthelps

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Lola Tash and Nicole Argiris on August 31, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'When someone is really testing you and you can just feel all the nice draining from your body'.

Photo by Lola Tash and Nicole Argiris on August 31, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'aubrey @aubreybell oh boy ever spill a little bit of your coffee and realize the thread you are hanging on by is actually quite thin'.
Photo by Lola Tash and Nicole Argiris on August 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'when you leave things for tomorrow and tomorrow arrives'.

Photo by Lola Tash and Nicole Argiris on August 29, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Mike Primavera @primawesome I'm thinking about quitting my job and pursuing anxiety full-time.'.

node.text: If you’re good at something never do it for free ✨ @primawesome

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Lola Tash and Nicole Argiris on August 28, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Some days I'm happy, but some days need to turn on TLC and watch a lady eat laundry detergent to to feel better about myself.'.

Photo by Lola Tash and Nicole Argiris on August 28, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Adulting is constantly saying "I'm not free that day, can you do this date?" Back and forth for 3 months.'.
